{{TAGDEF|NBSEEIG|[integer]|0}}

Description: {{TAG|NBSEEIG}} sets the number of BSE eigenvectors written to the {{FILE|BSEFATBAND}} file. If {{TAG|BSEHOLE}} or {{TAG|BSEELECTRON}} is set, {{TAG|NBSEEIG}} exciton wavefunctions are written to the {{FILE|CHG}}.XX files.
